{"tid":708024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Hehe 室內抽插冇拉窗簾 大批市民屋外圍觀","createTime":"2018-06-19T04:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T04:34:01.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81e6dd2ca5bfc5b2f8f3f5261cf24473477e3db8","tid":708024,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"隨著社會變得開放，市民普遍對於同性戀的看法也較以往更為包容，不過雖然口說接受，但當看到同志戀人親熱時，大部人難免仍然會感受到一陣「衝擊」。日前網上流傳一段影片，一對男同志戀人於室內親熱時因為沒有拉上窗簾，引起大批途人於屋外圍觀，不少人看到這個情境都感到非常震撼。<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的影片可見，事發地點應為上環文咸東街一幢住宅，當時一對戀人於靠近窗邊的位置親熱，其中一人躺平，另一名男子則在上方「活動」，兩人似乎太過投入，一直沒有注意沒有拉上窗簾，兩人的行為盡入外人眼簾，引來不少市民圍觀，部份人更舉機拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n這對戀人一直沒有理會他人目光，繼續沉醉於靈慾交流，兩人疑似完事後，採取主動的男子稍為離開現場，這時候一直躺平的另一人彎腰坐在床上，可以清楚看到這人蓄短髮，無疑是一張男生的臉孔，令不少圍觀的市民起哄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/06/19/e/e4c05ceb33faf4afdc78a99336eeaee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2Fe%2Fe4c05ceb33faf4afdc78a99336eeaee6.jpg&h=366cf1e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=NSOy7aoHwbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D3%26v%3DNSOy7aoHwbo&d=QUqEOzsMfh%2BFED0Ir7pZ1pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=58186cbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=3&amp;v=NSOy7aoHwbo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4419ec467640b0f242f5212fa4452948752ce931","tid":708024,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeed8647178228e32952f1f94b50c0f3ffd1885","tid":708024,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"See